                   How to Register Your Site as an Official Mirror


@{U}                                                                           @{UU}

Send e-mail to MikeWebb@CompuServe.COM with "Register AM Mirror" as the
subject, and specify the following information:
@{LINDENT 4}

*  A precise URL to be listed as the mirror site
*  An e-mail address to which new issues of AM can be sent, and with which
   we can communicate with you
*  A short description of the site
*  The format(s) you will be carrying (HTML online, AmigaGuide online,
