*  A country or general geographic location of the server supplying your
   site
@{LINDENT 0}


That's it! If we register your site as an official mirror site, you get a
listing in the mirrors.htm file that comes with every issue, and eventually
on The Webb Site itself. Thank you for supporting The Amiga Monitor.
