@{U}                                                                           @{UU}

Do you know about something important in the Amiga community that has been
overlooked? Is there a story you would like us to cover?

You can suggest something you would like to see covered in the pages of The
Amiga Monitor.

You can check the @{"Staff List" LINK staff} if you want to send
e-mail to the staff member who is most appropriate for the subject at hand,
or you can just send e-mail to the Publisher at MikeWebb@CompuServe.COM

