                         Submitting a Product For Review

@{U}                                                                           @{UU}

Product reviews are as important a part of a magazine as any other. Although
most products we review are those that we have purchased or otherwise
obtained for our own purposes, we often review products at the request of
the company or individual producing or developing them. If you have something
you would like us to review at The Amiga Monitor, you can contact us about
doing so.

If you would like to contact the member of the staff most appropriate to the
nature of your product directly, see the @{"Staff List" LINK staff}. Otherwise,
you can send e-mail to the Publisher.

